ai_summary.Response: This commit primarily involves updates to documentation for integrating Britive with Microsoft Entra ID. The changes refine instructions for configuring Britive for provisioning and single sign-on (SSO), clarifying steps and button names. Minor adjustments were also made to the wording in the tutorials.
